<dl id="n08036e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08036e">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08036e"> 36(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Caligula&apos;s houseboat / Nemi, gold barge</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Efforts are being made to induce Premier Mussolini to give the 5,000,000 lire required &hellip; to raise the two gorgeous <mark>house boats which the Emperor Caligula had built on Lake Nemi</mark> close on 2,000 years ago &hellip; these two marvels of Roman ship construction &hellip; are described as the most luxurious <mark>barges</mark> ever built &hellip; In their time they &hellip; were covered with <mark>gold</mark> leaves. <small> <a name="IT3jan24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#IT3jan24"><cite title="source">Irish Times</cite></a> (3 January 1924) 5/5</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
